## Unexpected Behavior

> Comments won't post - getting a 422 error

## Expected Behavior

> Able to make new comments

## Reproduce the Error

1) Clone this repo (from develop branch)
2) Start your rails server (rails s)
3) Run npm run start
4) Navigate to login (use "chrishaar" and "123456" for credentials)
5) Click "Hide | Show Comments" and try and adda new comment
6) Nothing happens

